summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Roanoke Street, from Federal Avenue North to Eleventh Avenue North, et al in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing under Ordinance No. 17202, creating Local Improvement District No. 1620 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
